{
  "stem": "268.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He wants to see you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, oh, my god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Your commander, he wants to see you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was-- I don't know what to-- I had no watch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had no idea what time it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It must have been midnight, maybe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we-- I quickly put on my wet pants and my, my jacket and, and shuffled along with these wooden shoes and came to the commandant's quarters.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he is nice and warm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He's sitting there, drinking whatever, Schnapps or whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he, he certainly was not skinny.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was-- he was-- his cheeks were red and puffy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And had-- he even had a stomach, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because you would see the guys eating well and-- off of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And his, his glazed eyes-- he was-- he was a German national.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was actually a commandant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he was a, a commandant in prison himself, political prisoner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But he was in charge of the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He-- the only one over him was the SS guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he says-- well, he had even a dog, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, and, and that's the first time I've seen a dog inside the camp, other than the SS men.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was kind of stroking him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he says, [GERMAN], and throws a harmonica at me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I caught it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I shouldn't have asked him-- you know, [GERMAN], what should it be?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you wish?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, [GERMAN] Schubert.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't play Schubert.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- the only Schubert I remember-- it was a serenade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it came when my uncle bought me my first chromatic harmonica.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he got me a book of songs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a Schubert song.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
